# Liabilities Insurance Policy Net Excluding Current Bonus Amount

## identifier
de4527

## type
float

## definition
Report the total  policy liability net of reinsurance as per prudential standards, excluding current year bonuses. Note that this differs to the accounting standards treatment.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.PolicyNetExcludingCurrentBonus.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
